headline: American Express Chairman and CEO Stephen J. Squeri to Participate in Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference
summary: NEW YORK, November 08, 2024--American Express Company (NYSE: AXP) Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Stephen J. Squeri will participate in the Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference in New York on Tuesday, December 10, 2024, at 09:20 a.m. Eastern. Mr. Squeri will participate in a fireside chat relating to the Company’s business strategy and financial performance.
